Package com.chembiohub.tpmap.dstruct

Class Protein2D

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chembiohub.tpmap.dstruct.Protein2D
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Protein
    public class Protein2D
extends java.lang.Object
implements Protein
    The Protein class defines an individual protein, including it's accession, name, organism name, description. This class also holds 2x2 matrices for each Replicate x TMT for: - Absolute values - Relative values - Relative values normalised TP-MAP scores and P-values are stored for the protein.
